 EUTMR) and was deceptive (Article 59(1)(a) in conjunction with Article 7(1)(g) EUTMR).","entityClasses":["35 41 43"],"earlierName":"(Trade mark without text)","entityResult":"Trade mark declared invalid","deemedDeliveredToAppellantDate":"23/03/2026","deemedDeliveredToDefendantDate":"23/03/2026"}],"numFound":1820}